          <VULN_ATTRIBUTE>Fix_Text</VULN_ATTRIBUTE>
          <ATTRIBUTE_DATA>Configure the VPN Gateway to limit the number of concurrent sessions for user accounts to 1 or to an organization-defined number, as documented in the SSP.</ATTRIBUTE_DATA>
